- I'm going to stop it.

313
00:16:24,824 --> 00:16:27,941
Quite simple, get yourself
adopted as a candidate,

314
00:16:28,104 --> 00:16:31,255
win a general election,
serve on the back benches,

315
00:16:32,104 --> 00:16:34,982
become a Minister
and repeal the act.

316
00:16:35,664 --> 00:16:38,383
The badgers might be
getting on a bit by then.

317
00:16:39,904 --> 00:16:42,543
Assistant Secretaries
reporting to the Minister!

318
00:16:42,704 --> 00:16:43,704
I know.

319
00:16:43,864 --> 00:16:46,298
Does he think
he is a civil servant?

320
00:16:47,144 --> 00:16:49,214
The arrogance
of these politicians!

321
00:16:49,424 --> 00:16:50,618
Ah, Bernard.

322
00:16:53,264 --> 00:16:54,264
Thank you.

323
00:16:55,584 --> 00:16:56,937
Yes.

324
00:16:58,304 --> 00:16:59,419
