Ours is the fourword trick.

356
00:18:21,984 --> 00:18:26,296
There are fourwords if you want
a Ministerto accept a proposal.

357
00:18:26,464 --> 00:18:29,740
Quick. Simple. Popular. Cheap.

358
00:18:30,704 --> 00:18:33,013
And there are fourwords
fora proposal

359
00:18:33,184 --> 00:18:34,936
if you want it thrown out.

360
00:18:35,464 --> 00:18:38,695
Complicated. Lengthy.
Expensive. Controversial.

361
00:18:39,664 --> 00:18:42,940
And to be really sure
the Ministerdoesn't accept it,

362
00:18:43,104 --> 00:18:45,254
