is courageous.

363
00:18:45,424 --> 00:18:47,096
Worse than "controversial".

364
00:18:49,344 --> 00:18:51,778
"Controversial" means
"this'll lose yourvotes".

365
00:18:51,944 --> 00:18:55,016
