the badgerprotest.

389
00:20:33,064 --> 00:20:35,339
- I thought itwas over.
- She and herboyfriend.

390
00:20:35,504 --> 00:20:38,416
A 24 hour"Save the badgers"
vigil in Hayward's Spinney

391
00:20:38,584 --> 00:20:40,336
unless protection is restored.

392
00:20:40,504 --> 00:20:43,701
And they announcing it
to the press at 5.00 p. m.

393
00:20:43,864 --> 00:20:47,015
"Minister's daughter
in badgerprotest vigil".

394
00:20:48,064 --> 00:20:50,703
