more than a little embarrassed.

396
00:20:54,584 --> 00:20:57,860
"Minister's daughter in nude
badgerprotest vigil".

397
00:20:58,424 --> 00:20:59,459
What!

398
00:20:59,624 --> 00:21:01,899
Miss Hacker
and herboyfriend will be...

