this makes it a big story.

403
00:21:19,064 --> 00:21:20,941
Front page: with photograph.

404
00:21:23,224 --> 00:21:24,418
Hello, Humphrey.

405
00:21:26,984 --> 00:21:28,497
Something the matter?

406
00:21:30,024 --> 00:21:31,024
