407
00:21:31,864 --> 00:21:34,378
Shall we say a slight
embarrassment, Minister?

408
00:21:34,664 --> 00:21:35,664
How slight?

409
00:21:36,264 --> 00:21:39,939
Withoutwishing in any sense
to overstate the case

410
00:21:40,944 --> 00:21:44,414
orcause undue alarm,
nevertheless, the fact remains...

