something to exhibit.

429
00:22:40,864 --> 00:22:43,697
- How do you mean?
- It's to be a nude protest vigil.

430
00:22:43,944 --> 00:22:45,013
I see.

431
00:22:45,264 --> 00:22:48,097
- Thatwould make the front pages!
- Yes, quite so.

432
00:22:48,544 --> 00:22:50,774
The press just mustn't find out.

433
00:22:50,944 --> 00:22:54,016
I don't know
what gets into these students.

434
00:22:54,184 --> 00:22:57,142
- It's appalling. They're shameless.
- Indeed, Minister.

435
00:22:57,304 --> 00:22:58,896
