the parents fault.

440
00:23:09,784 --> 00:23:11,183
Of course it is!

441
00:23:11,984 --> 00:23:13,337
Authority, Humphrey.

442
00:23:13,504 --> 00:23:15,222
All this is an indictment

443
00:23:15,384 --> 00:23:17,659
