of discipline.

444
00:23:18,144 --> 00:23:22,422
So they just take it out
on innocent people like me.

445
00:23:23,744 --> 00:23:26,656
- Who are they?
- We know the young lady's name.

446
00:23:26,824 --> 00:23:28,621
Lady!
Who is she?

447
00:23:29,184 --> 00:23:31,220
