could lock her in herroom?

464
00:24:25,424 --> 00:24:28,097
Annie's out atwork.
What about the police?

465
00:24:28,264 --> 00:24:31,097
"Ministersets police
on nude daughter".

466
00:24:31,264 --> 00:24:33,824
I'm not sure that completely
kills the story.

467
00:24:33,984 --> 00:24:37,897
- There must be something.
- Perhaps if I look at the files...

468
00:24:38,064 --> 00:24:40,817
My daughter's about to get
page one of the Sun,

469
00:24:40,984 --> 00:24:44,260
and probably page three,
and you just think of the files.

470
00:24:44,424 --> 00:24:46,858
- Nevertheless...
- They're all out there.

471
00:24:48,224 --> 00:24:50,738
- What angle they'll take?
- Wide angle.

472
00:24:53,104 --> 00:24:55,618
