wish to make a statement?".

474
00:24:58,384 --> 00:25:00,944
"Is the Hackerfamily getting
too much exposure?".

475
00:25:01,184 --> 00:25:03,414
"Is the Ministertrying
to conduct a coverup?".

476
00:25:03,584 --> 00:25:06,462
