484
00:25:30,584 --> 00:25:32,142
It's foryou, Minister.

485
00:25:33,144 --> 00:25:34,577
Lucy. Hello, darling.

486
00:25:34,904 --> 00:25:36,337
- Hello, Daddy.
- I got yournote.

487
00:25:36,504 --> 00:25:38,495
